N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 §§ 85-2.15 - Dismissal of an application

State Regulations

Whenever it shall appear that the statutory requirements
for a certificate cannot be met, the commission may dismiss the application and
terminate the proceedings upon the motion of any party or staff counsel, or
upon its own motion. Notes
